title: What The Heck Do You Want?
itunes:title: What The Heck Do You Want?
description:
Episode 428 - If I asked you where exactly do you want to be in 5 years, could you give me an exact answer and tell me exactly how you will get there? Most people can't. In this episode, I help you get clarity on your life through journaling, which I feel is one of the most important daily routines that we can have.
